N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 451.190 - Nominal account

State Regulations

Any of the accounts the balances of which are transferred
to retained earnings at the close of each fiscal year; so-called because such
accounts reflect completed transactions or expired costs. Notes
